Lecture - 2:
user theke amra kono likhito detail pabo na...bikkhipto info theke amader real
jinishpati ber kore anta hobe. It is part of training.

Sub system niye kaj korte hobe, jegula major sub system arki. jemon receive
kora, han tan...

Ruhan asks: initially jokhon amra design korbo, tokhon ki ekta subsystem k use 
case hishebe chinta korbo?
answer: 

master data:
jei data gulo common, shobar jonno, jemon windows os er font size, resolution 
etc..
item info, item category, egula master data for a supply chain ...
ei master data guloke alada vabe handle kora lagbe.
ei master data manage korar jonno muloto 1 ta use case thake. amra 1 tai rakhbo.
oto detaile jano na.

class starts:
OWSP (or OWASP whatever) holo security niye kotha barta hoy emon forum, check 
that out.

Properties of Secure Software:

Confidentiality:
- sensitive info encrypted thakbe. keu jate egula access na korte
pare...hash kore rakha etc. etc.

Integrity:
- authencity ba bisshashjoggota. jemon, porikkhar number jodi illegaly keu 
change kore felte pare, taile oi system tar Integrity kom. Eta handle er jonno
hoyto log rakha hoy (kobe, k, ki change korse). tarpor notification ashe, google
account e login korle jemon mail ashe.

Availability:
- kokhono down hobe na. master - slave, etc...

Non-repudiation:
k ei kaj ta korlo tar ekta proof, jate osshikar korte na pare.

Authencitaion:
eta ar ki likhbo

slide e dekhi lekhai ase besh kichu...

